preconditions
have python installed

Commands:
    - python --version
    - pip install pytest
    - pytest    (to execute all the test that are contained in the folder) '.' = test passed
    - pytest -v     (more specifically results)
    - pytest -m nameOfMark (execute all test that are using this mark)

Recommendations:
    - pytest command recognize all the functions that contains "test" keyword at the beginning of the func name
    - take care with the names of the files, function and classes do you create